---
layout: base.njk
title: The E-commerce Director's Cut — Mobile1st
description: "The E-commerce Director's Cut: practical, opinionated writing on experimentation, personalization, and Revenue Per Visitor from the Mobile1st team."
---

<div class="news-index__header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="news-index__hero">
      <p class="podcast-index__eyebrow">The Newsletter</p>
      <h1 class="news-index__title">The E-Commerce Director's Cut</h1>
      <p class="news-index__description">Practical, opinionated writing on experimentation, personalization, and Revenue Per Visitor. Read by Directors of E-Commerce at brands doing $5M–$100M.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="blog-listing">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="blog-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="blog-card">
        <div class="blog-card-meta">
          <span class="blog-card-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
          {% if post.data.author %}<span class="blog-card-author">{{ post.data.author }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <h2 class="blog-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        {% if post.data.description %}
        <p class="blog-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="blog-card-cta">Read post →</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
